### Transformation Rules Applied

- All entities inherit from [AuditableEntity](file:///c:/Users/Admin/source/Workspaces/2026/Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026/Vns-Epr-Blazor-2026/Vns.Erp.Domain/Common/AuditableEntity.cs#6-11) (not XPO `AuditableBaseObject`)
- Removed all XAF/XPO attributes (`XafDisplayName`, `RuleRequiredField`, `RuleUniqueValue`, `DefaultClassOptions`, etc.)
- Removed all [OnSaving()](file:///C:/Users/Admin/source/Workspaces/2026/Vns-Erp-xaf-2026/src/Vns-Erp-xaf-2026/Vns_Erp_xaf_2026.Module/BusinessObjects/MasterData/Company/Department.cs#139-150) auto-code logic (to be reimplemented in Application layer)
- Removed `ITreeNode` interface implementations (XAF-specific)
- Removed all `[NotMapped]` computed display properties (UI concerns)
- Replaced `MediaDataObject` references with `byte[]`
- Converted `IList<T>` / `ObservableCollection<T>` to `ICollection<T>` / `List<T>`
- Added explicit FK properties (e.g., `CompanyId`, `BranchId`) for EF Core

### Verification

- **Build**: `dotnet build Vns.Erp.Domain` → ✅ 0 errors, 0 warnings
